WEBVTT

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:32.056
for me and everyone
growing up at that time,

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:33.280
including boys.

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:37.896
She frequently shares the story
of how a young boy approached her

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.936
after a couple of terms in office

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:43.856
and asked, "Can boys
really grow up to be president?"

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:46.016
(Laughter)

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:48.816
Role models really matter,

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:51.656
but even with such strong role models

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:53.976
who I am so grateful for,

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.856
when I was encouraged
to run for president,

00:01:56.880 --> 00:02:02.216
my first reaction was,
"Who am I to run for president?